c: 33
v: 33
t: "Hlalani\temizini\tyenu ningaqhayisi\tngemizimba\tyenu njengokuqhayisa kwamandulo kwamaxesha okungazi. Nimisele iSalâh,\tninikele ngeZakâh\tnithobele uAllâh\tnoMthunywa\twaKhe\tUAllâh\tUfuna ukususa ukungahlambululeki kuphela kuni bantu bendlu (yoMprofeti) nokunihlambulula ngentlambuluko efezekileyo"